        "pitch_and_presentation": 4
    },

    "final_verdict": "The Personal Declutter App shows potential but requires significant refinement to be competitive. Recommendations: 1) Develop unique features that clearly differentiate it from existing solutions, 2) Strengthen and document the technical implementation, particularly around AI integration, 3) Improve the presentation with demos, screenshots, and market analysis, 4) Conduct user testing and incorporate feedback, 5) Focus on one or two standout features rather than trying to do everything. The project earns a composite score of 5/10, reflecting both its potential and current limitations. While the 48-hour development is impressive, the project needs more development time to become a viable product."
